        <body><div type="bibliography">
                
                <p>Never published before this edition.</p>
            </div><div type="edition" xml:lang="grc" xml:space="preserve">
                
                <ab>
                    <lb n="0"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/><certainty locus="name" match=".."/>
                    <lb n="1"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>ε</orig> <space quantity="3" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="2"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig><unclear>σ</unclear>υ</orig><orig><choice><unclear>ν</unclear><unclear>μ</unclear></choice></orig> 
                    <lb n="3"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig><unclear>ν</unclear>ερ</orig> <space quantity="2" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="4"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig><unclear>ν</unclear>ευ</orig> <space quantity="2" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="5"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>ονχ</orig> <space quantity="2" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="6"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <w lemma="ἴδιος">ἰδίαν</w> <space quantity="1" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="7"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig><unclear>σ</unclear>νο</orig> <space quantity="2" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="8"/><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><orig>νκ</orig> <space quantity="2" unit="character"/>
                    <lb n="8a"/><space extent="unknown" unit="line"/>
                </ab>
            </div><div type="apparatus" xml:space="preserve">
            
                <p/>
               </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="fr">
            <p>Intraduisible.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="en">
            <p>Not usefully translatable.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="it">
            <p>Intraducibile.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="ar">
            <p/>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
             <p>The very small groups of letters preserved on this fragment do not plausibly belong to personal names. Only one word is recognisable (<foreign xml:lang="grc">ἰδίαν</foreign>) and would perhaps suggest a decree honouring someone for his 
                 'proper' virtue, devotion of other quality. Alternatively, one might suggest the phrase <foreign xml:lang="grc">κατ᾿ἰδίαν</foreign> 'from his own expense', which is often mentioned 
                 about the deeds of a benefactor. Both would imply that the inscription was a decree of honours. The text was laid out in full lines with no account of the limits of syllables. Its language might be either dialect or koine.</p>
            </div></body>
    </text>
